questionsAndAnswers.answer:
1) I need hosting and domain login details (most important). 
2) Full information about your online store,Product & image of your company!

questionsAndAnswers.question: I am interested in your Gig,Can I order it?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes. But, first make sure you contacted me to see if I am able to do your job. It saves us both a lot of time and money!

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you solve the issue problems after the order is marked done?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, your Satisfaction is my priority. My main goal is to have clients that can depend on me as clients are the biggest assets in any business. to do that I always walk the extra mile.

questionsAndAnswers.answer: -Yes.Don't worry.Without coding you can edit or update your website as well as 100% Easily editable and I will provide you a video for maintenance it.
